methods.name: refreshDisplayName
methods.description: Force the displayed name to refresh, by firing PlayerEvent.NameFormat , using the real player name as event parameter.

methods.name: setForcedPose
methods.description: Force a pose for the player. If set, the vanilla pose determination and clearance check is skipped. Make sure the pose is clear yourself (e.g. in PlayerTick). This has to be set just once, do not set it every tick. Make sure to clear (null) the pose if not required anymore and only use if necessary.
